# ===============================================
# IMPORTANT REMINDERS
# ===============================================
# This .gitignore helps prevent accidental commits of:
# 1. Credentials (DB passwords, API keys, JWT secrets)
# 2. SSL/TLS certificates and private keys
# 3. Local configuration files
# 4. Sensitive data (databases, logs with PII)
# 5. IDE-specific files
#
# Always review what you're committing:
#   git status
#   git diff
#
# Before committing, ensure:
# ✅ No .env files
# ✅ No passwords in properties files
# ✅ No API keys or secrets
# ✅ No SSL certificates
# ===============================================
